	</nav>
    <p>Since it first appeared on Earth 3 years ago, the crystallized form of cosmic energy called "stardust" has been a source of incredible, but often unstable, power. A bioterrorist organization plans to use it to raise an army of cosmic super-soldiers, but their one successful specimen has broken out of captivity. Blue Haze hopes to track it down and make sure such a powerful bio-weapon doesn't fall back into enemy hands, but it's cunning creator will stop at nothing to reclaim the monster she's created...
    </p>
